events.name: Online: Introduction to Machine Learning
events.description:
Please Note:
Due to the critical circumstances of COVID-19, this is an online event. Please stay at home and experience learning like in real-time from experienced speakers.

This is a free event powered by GDG Kandahar. The event will be streamed live from our Youtube channel and Facebook page. Please subscribe to our youtube channel and like our Facebook page to get a notification when the live stream starts.

The agenda for the event will be shared later.

Youtube:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC0W6dtNnNlXqK2zN8htibDw

Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/gdgkandahar

group_profile.intro: I am the GDG Kandahar Organizer and an assistant professor at the computer science faculty of Kandahar University. I am interested to provide the opportunity for tech enthusiasts to come together and share their knowledge and experience.
